com.robopupu.api.dependency

Class DependenciesCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.robopupu.api.dependency.DependenciesCache

  • public class DependenciesCache
extends java.lang.Object
    DependenciesCache is used for saving and restoring DependencyScopes for their DependencyScopeOwners, and for saving and accessing DependencyMaps using String based keys. Views have a dedicated method View.getViewTag() for providing the key.
